OL,3,CPressures across Cardiff hospitals
OL,4,Cafter 'huge spike' in emergency
OL,5,Cattendances
OL,7,FA Welsh health board has said it has
OL,8,Fseen a "huge spike" in the number of
OL,9,Fpeople coming to a Cardiff emergency
OL,10,Fdepartment.
OL,12,FCardiff and Vale University Health
OL,13,FBoard said it has seen over 200 more
OL,14,Fpeople presenting at the University
OL,15,FHospital of Wales emergency department
OL,16,Fthan they would usually expect.
OL,18,FThe health board is urging the public
OL,19,Fto only attend the department in an
OL,20,Femergency and to be prepared for a
OL,21,Flonger wait than usual.
