OL,3,CPressures across Cardiff hospitals
OL,4,Cafter 'huge spike' in emergency
OL,5,Cattendances
OL,7,F"This influx in attendances has caused
OL,8,Fsignificant pressure across both
OL,9,FUniversity Hospital of Wales and
OL,10,FUniversity Hospital Llandough and has
OL,11,Fresulted in incredibly long waits in
OL,12,Fthe department and for admission to a
OL,13,Fhospital bed," a statement from the
OL,14,Fhealth board posted on social media
OL,15,Fread.
OL,17,F"We are urging the public to please
OL,18,Fonly attend the emergency unit in an
OL,19,Femergency. If you do need to attend,
OL,20,Fplease be prepared for a longer wait
OL,21,Fthan usual."
