OL,3,CPressures across Cardiff hospitals
OL,4,Cafter 'huge spike' in emergency
OL,5,Cattendances
OL,7,FThe health board advised the public to
OL,8,Fuse NHS 111 Wales if they are unsure
OL,9,Fwhat healthcare support they need.
OL,11,F"We thank you for your ongoing support
OL,12,Fduring this challenging time and
OL,13,Fplease remember to treat all
OL,14,Fcolleagues and patients with kindness
OL,15,Fand respect," the statement said.
